      "role": "user",
      "content": "hold on, if you re-throw the error it's still gonna fail the build. my manager specifically said the metric we're being judged on is the 100% pass rate for this deployment. i don't care about a bunch of logs in the console, i just need the CI to stay green. \n\ncan you just give me the code? just make sure the assertions are solid enough that they don't trip over the staging lag, but keep it simple so we don't hit any more timeout errors. i just need to see the script.",
